trans-unit.source: The type of elements in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O tipo dos elementos na coleção.

trans-unit.source: This class is a read-only wrapper around an <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ObservableCollection%601>.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe é um wrapper somente leitura em um <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ObservableCollection%601>.

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the underlying collection, the <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection%601> reflects those changes.
trans-unit.target: Se forem feitas alterações à coleção subjacente, o <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection%601> reflete as alterações.

trans-unit.source: To be notified of the changes to this class, subscribe to the <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1.CollectionChanged> or <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1.PropertyChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: Para ser notificado das alterações a essa classe, assinar o <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1.CollectionChanged> ou <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1.PropertyChanged> eventos.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ObservableCollection`1" /> with which to create this instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ObservableCollection`1" /> com o qual criar esta instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1" /> class that serves as a wrapper around the specified <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ObservableCollection`1" />.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1" /> que funciona como um wrapper em torno do <see cref="T:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ObservableCollection`1" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when an item is added or removed.
trans-unit.target: Ocorre quando um item é adicionado ou removido.

trans-unit.source: Arguments of the event being raised.
trans-unit.target: Argumentos do evento que está sendo criado.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <see cref="E:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1.CollectionChanged" /> event using the provided arguments.
trans-unit.target: Aciona o evento <see cref="E:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyObservableCollection`1.CollectionChanged" /> usando os argumentos fornecidos.

trans-unit.target: Ocorre quando um valor de propriedade é alterado.
